    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Compression scheme designed to reduce storage requirements of digital video. MPEG is an acronym for Motion Pictures Experts Group, a committee of the International Standards Organization.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
